{"tid":1053244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家做緊銀行","createTime":"2019-03-09T01:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T07:46:30.000Z","uid":222261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c362aa04cfcdb00153199061a75de71db01728","tid":1053244,"uid":222261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲人成日話銀行福利好又點又點<br />\n其實好刻薄<br />\n話就話一個月有兩日有薪病假<br />\n但其實根本唔會俾你請病假<br />\n發緊燒都要你番去坐<br />\n<br />\n公司仲話有幾日考試假<br />\n但公司要你去考試就會放你大假或者輪休個假<br />\n<br />\n番工覺得好凍 想閂細啲冷氣<br />\n佢地會問「係你凍定係啲客凍阿？」<br />\n係你覺得凍就自己諗辦法<br />\n貼暖包又好咩都好<br />\n<br />\n番工時間話就話8點半至6點<br />\n但永遠都成7點先走得<br />\n就算你係完全冇野做<br />\n佢都唔會俾你走<br />\n坐係度成個鐘<br />\n好似玩緊困獸鬥咁<br />\n<br />\n宜家個職位根本未洗跑數<br />\n但佢就會一直叫你考牌考牌要幫手跑數<br />\n跑完啲數仲要唔會計落自己條數度<br />\n<br />\n究竟一個bba fg唔做銀行會唔會有更好既選擇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7999475b93ccda4c2c662abaa4bffe51f23d5eab","tid":1053244,"uid":198165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:22:42.000Z","msg":"Retail banking 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a7ae91c357a4a100e1b01592866265438fd37b","tid":1053244,"uid":222261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7999475b93ccda4c2c662abaa4bffe51f23d5eab","tid":1053244,"uid":198165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:22:42.000Z","msg":"Retail banking 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:46:30.000Z","msg":"咁究竟有冇其他出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}